[SHORT DESC]
Transforms Shaymin into Shaymin-S.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>When used on a Shaymin it will change forme into Shaymin-S. Gracidea can't be used if the Shaymin is frozen or at night. The forme change will be reversed if the Pokemon becomes frozen, night falls, or it is placed in the Pokemon Storage System. Cannot be activated in Link or Wi-Fi Battles.</p>